# Changelog

All notable changes to SAPEED will be documented in this file.

The format is based on Keep a Changelog.
This project adheres to Semantic Versioning (SemVer).

---

## [1.0.0] - 2026-02-28

### Added
- Full Streamlit dashboard for evaluation analysis.
- Student-level dimension scoring.
- Institutional benchmark calculation (student-weighted mean).
- 95% confidence interval estimation for benchmarking.
- Dimension-level classification (Above / Within / Below Institutional Range).
- Cronbach's alpha per dimension.
- Stratified alpha (institutional level).
- Multilevel correlation analysis:
  - Student pooled
  - Professor ecological
  - Within selected professor
- Ridge regression with K-Fold cross-validation.
- Regularization curve visualization.
- Coefficient stability paths.
- Complete technical documentation (Wiki).
- Governance and responsible use framework.
- Internal technical appendix.
- Synthetic demo dataset support.

### Fixed
- Initial stable institutional release.

---

## [Unreleased]

### Planned
- Cluster-robust confidence intervals.
- GroupKFold for Ridge modeling.
- Optional Spearman correlation.
- Leave-one-professor-out institutional benchmark.
- Bootstrap-based inference.